data.description: LOOK no further! A 2002 Diamond Condition Colonial has it all.You enter this home from the Front Porch into a Sunny Foyer.The first floor has both a FLR, Family Room and EIK with Double Ovens, Granite Counter Tops with Complimenting Glass Backsplash, DR, Laundry Room, Office and Half Bath. The second floor has a Primary Bedroom with Ensuite, Jacuzzi Tub and Separate Walk In Shower, Double Vanity Sinks. There are 3 Additional Bedrooms, and an Additional Full Bath, Bonus Room with a door leading to a Full Walk Up Attic. A Full Finished Walk Out Basement with A/C, a Separate Entrance with a Private Patio. This space is Sunny and Bright with multiple rooms, a 2 Car Attached Garage. This property has 3 beautifully landscaped acres and Mature Planting. The back yard features a Deck accessed thru the kitchen,not to mention a 29 X 50 Above Ground Pool,Sheds for Storage,Electric and Cable Buried Underground, Curtain Drains to keep it safe from all the elements. Minutes to the Taconic and 84.AMAZING!
